						<summary>

						<p>This is much damaged. It records a gift of gold for burning a perpetual land in the temple of Kūḍal-Āḻvār by a queen of <hi rend="bold">Mummuḍichchōḻa-Perumāḷ</hi>, whose name cannot be properly made out. This is evidently an inscription of Rājēndra-Chōḷa I.</p>						

						</summary>
